    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. CFD model accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device tolerance study. Note: REQ-HEM-01 (RH < 1.0 for all points) and REQ-HEM-02 (RH ≥ 1.0 for at least one point) were both bound to the hemolysis acceptance claim; the observed RH range of 0.82–0.97 satisfies REQ-HEM-01 but violates REQ-HEM-02, creating an unresolved requirement conflict that was not flagged prior to acceptance.",
